         <component>
            <section>
               <id root="2a804ee8-e519-4569-a75a-9b75f16131e6"/>
               <code code="34089-3" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DESCRIPTION SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Each Tablet Contains:</paragraph>
                  <table width="30%">
                     <col width="80%" align="left" valign="middle"/>
                     <col width="20%" align="right" valign="middle"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <tr styleCode="Toprule Botrule">
                           <td>Acetaminophen</td>
                           <td>500 mg</td>
                        </tr>
                     </tbody>
                  </table>
                  <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="MM1"/>
                  <table width="30%">
                     <col width="80%" align="left" valign="middle"/>
                     <col width="20%" align="right" valign="middle"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <tr styleCode="Toprule Botrule">
                           <td>Phenyltoloxamine Citrate</td>
                           <td>55 mg</td>
                        </tr>
                     </tbody>
                  </table>
                  <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="MM2"/>
                  <paragraph>Acetaminophen, 4'-hydroxyacetanilide, a slightly bitter, white odorless, crystalline powder, is a non-opiate, non-salicylate analgesic and antipyretic.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Phenyltoloxamine citrate is an antihistamine having the chemical name <content styleCode="italics">N</content>, <content styleCode="italics">N</content>-dimethyl-2-(α-phenyl-<content styleCode="italics">o</content>-tolyloxy) ethylamine dihydrogen citrate.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Inactive ingredients: Each tablet contains povidone, microcrystalline cellulose, sodium starch glycolate and magnesium stearate.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20100412"/>
               <component>
                  <observationMedia ID="MM1">
